These are Puzzles for 4x2 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-1::.
2 different games are played: bridge, poker
The people have 2 different jobs:  designer, social-worker
There are 2 different favourite colors: lilac, blood-red
The people use 2 different means of transport: bike, jet-ski
1. the person playing bridge is on the far right##1
2. the person who likes lilac is on the right of the person driving the jet-ski##1
3. the designer is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |       1       |     2     |
| Game       | poker       | bridge |
| Job         | social-worker | designer  |
| Color       | blood-red    | lilac    |
| Transport   | jet-ski       | bike      |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-2::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, lemonade
2 different brands of cigars are smoked: cain, pall-mall
The people perfer 2 different movie-genres: action, time-travel
The people's birthday is in 2 different months: december, october
1. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person who's birthday is in december##1
2. the cain-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person watching action movies is on the right of the person drinking lemonade##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |      2      |
| Beverage      | lemonade     | almond-milk |
| Cigar           | cain | pall-mall      |
| Movie-Genre   | time-travel  | action      |
| Birthday         | december | october     |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-3::.
There are 2 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, soy-milk
House: cape-cod, craftsman
2 different pets are kept: guinea-pig, cat
The people use 2 different means of transport: quad-bike, taxi
1. the owner of the cat is on the left of the person drinking soy-milk##1
2. the person drinking iced-tea is the person driving the taxi##1
3. the cape-cod house is on the far left##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |
| Beverage      | iced-tea | soy-milk  |
| House          | cape-cod    | craftsman   |
| Pet   | cat  | guinea-pig   |
| Transport     | taxi     | quad-bike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-4::.
2 different games are played: monopoly, canasta
There 2 different types of food: lemon, papaya
The people have 2 different jobs:  nurse, security-guard
The people prefer 2 different types of sport: swimming, rugby
1. the person who's sport is swimming is on the far left##1
2. the nurse is on the right of the person playing monopoly##1
3. the person playing canasta is the person eating lemon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |
| Game      | monopoly       | canasta |
| Food          | papaya         | lemon    |
| Job           | security-guard | nurse    |
| Sport   | swimming           | rugby   |

