.:: Puzzle 4x2-Level-1-20::.
The people have 2 different jobs:  coach, security-guard
House: art-deco, futuristic
2 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit
The people have 2 different hobbies: magic-tricks, chess
1. the coach is on the right of the art-deco house##1
2. the coach is on the right of the person who's hobby is chess##1
3. the owner of the mouse is the security-guard##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |     2     |
| Job           | security-guard | coach     |
| House   | art-deco          | futuristic |
| Pet           | mouse          | rabbit    |
| Hobby     | chess            | magic-tricks       |

 